                          <span class="text-sm text-text-body">Submit via the online button on https://www.roundrocktexas.gov/city-departments/municipal-court/driving-safety-courses/ — complete the Driver's Safety Request form and upload. Also upload driver's license and current proof of insurance. Check email for correspondence; failure to respond to email will result in denial.</span>
                          <a href="https://www.roundrocktexas.gov/city-departments/municipal-court/driving-safety-courses/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-xs text-primary hover:underline break-all mt-0.5">www.roundrocktexas.gov/city-departments/municipal-court/driving-safety-courses</a>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Required Documents -->
                <div class="bg-surface-muted border border-border rounded-[14px] p-4 flex flex-col gap-4">
                  <div>
                    <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-text-body uppercase tracking-wide mb-2">To Request Approval — Submit These</p>
                    <ul class="flex flex-col gap-1.5 list-none m-0 p-0">
                      <li class="text-sm text-text-body flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 shrink-0">•</span><span>Completed Driver's Safety Request form (printed by clerk if in-person; downloadable in English or Spanish if by mail; uploaded if online)</span></li>
                      <li class="text-sm text-text-body flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 shrink-0">•</span><span>Valid Texas driver's license (paper copy required for in-person/mail; upload for online)</span></li>
                      <li class="text-sm text-text-body flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 shrink-0">•</span><span>Current proof of financial responsibility (liability insurance) valid on the day of request — must provide a paper copy</span></li>
                      <li class="text-sm text-text-body flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 shrink-0">•</span><span>Signed legal affidavit stating you have not taken a driving safety course for another citation dismissed within the past 12 months</span></li>
                      <li class="text-sm text-text-body flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 shrink-0">•</span><span>Payment of court costs ($144 regular / $169 school zone)</span></li>
                    </ul>
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-text-body uppercase tracking-wide mb-2">After Completing the Course — Submit These</p>
                    <ul class="flex flex-col gap-1.5 list-none m-0 p-0">
                      <li class="text-sm text-text-body flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 shrink-0">•</span><span>After course completion: DSC Certificate of Completion (TDLR-approved)</span></li>
                      <li class="text-sm text-text-body flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 shrink-0">•</span><span>After course completion: Type 3A Driving Record from Texas DPS</span></li>
                    </ul>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Important Notes -->
                <div class="bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-[14px] p-4 flex flex-col gap-2">
                  <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-amber-800">Important Deadlines &amp; Local Rules</p>
                  <ul class="flex flex-col gap-1.5 list-none m-0 p-0">
                    <li class="text-sm text-amber-900 flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 shrink-0">•</span><span>No later than the appearance date on your citation; mail requests must be postmarked no later than the appearance date</span></li>
                    <li class="text-sm text-amber-900 flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 shrink-0">•</span><span>You have 90 days from court approval to complete all requirements to complete the course and submit all documents.</span></li>
                    <li class="text-sm text-amber-900 flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 shrink-0">•</span><span>Verbatim from court site: 'Do not take a driving safety course without first requesting by one of the methods below.'</span></li>
                    <li class="text-sm text-amber-900 flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 shrink-0">•</span><span>Verbatim from court site: 'Make your request no later than the appearance date on your citation.'</span></li>
                    <li class="text-sm text-amber-900 flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 shrink-0">•</span><span>Verbatim from court site: 'Once request is made, you will have 90 days to complete all requirements.'</span></li>
                    <li class="text-sm text-amber-900 flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 shrink-0">•</span><span>Verbatim from court site: 'If you fail to provide complete information as requested, your plea will not be accepted.'</span></li>
                  </ul>
                </div>

                <!-- Forms -->
                <div>
                  <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-text mb-3">Court Forms &amp; Resources</p>
                  <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
                    <a href="https://www.roundrocktexas.gov/city-departments/municipal-court/driving-safety-courses/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="bg-surface-muted border border-border rounded-[10px] p-4 flex items-center gap-3 no-underline hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors group">
                      <svg class="w-[18px] h-[18px] shrink-0 text-primary" viewBox="0 0 18 18" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M10.5 2.25H5.25A1.5 1.5 0 0 0 3.75 3.75v10.5a1.5 1.5 0 0 0 1.5 1.5h7.5a1.5 1.5 0 0 0 1.5-1.5V6.75L10.5 2.25z"/><polyline points="10.5 2.25 10.5 6.75 14.25 6.75"/></svg>
                      <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-primary group-hover:underline">DSC Request Form (English)</span>
                    </a>
                    <a href="https://www.roundrocktexas.gov/city-departments/municipal-court/driving-safety-courses/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="bg-surface-muted border border-border rounded-[10px] p-4 flex items-center gap-3 no-underline hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors group">
                      <svg class="w-[18px] h-[18px] shrink-0 text-primary" viewBox="0 0 18 18" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M10.5 2.25H5.25A1.5 1.5 0 0 0 3.75 3.75v10.5a1.5 1.5 0 0 0 1.5 1.5h7.5a1.5 1.5 0 0 0 1.5-1.5V6.75L10.5 2.25z"/><polyline points="10.5 2.25 10.5 6.75 14.25 6.75"/></svg>
                      <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-primary group-hover:underline">DSC Request Form (Spanish)</span>
                    </a>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Contact -->
                <div class="bg-surface-muted border border-border rounded-[14px] p-4 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
                  <div class="bg-white rounded-[10px] p-4 flex flex-col gap-1">
                    <span class="text-xs text-text-body font-medium uppercase tracking-wide">Phone</span>
                    <a href="tel:5122185480" class="text-sm font-semibold text-primary hover:underline">(512) 218-5480</a>
                  </div>
                  <div class="bg-white rounded-[10px] p-4 flex flex-col gap-1">
                    <span class="text-xs text-text-body font-medium uppercase tracking-wide">Email</span>
                    <a href="mailto:rrcourt@roundrocktexas.gov" class="text-sm font-semibold text-primary hover:underline break-all">rrcourt@roundrocktexas.gov</a>
                  </div>
                  <div class="bg-white rounded-[10px] p-4 flex flex-col gap-1 sm:col-span-2">
                    <span class="text-xs text-text-body font-medium uppercase tracking-wide">Website</span>
                    <a href="https://www.roundrocktexas.gov/city-departments/municipal-court/driving-safety-courses/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-sm font-semibold text-primary hover:underline break-all">www.roundrocktexas.gov/city-departments/municipal-court/driving-safety-courses</a>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Always verify -->
                <div class="bg-surface-muted border border-border rounded-[14px] p-4 flex items-start gap-3">
                  <svg class="w-[18px] h-[18px] shrink-0 mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 18 18" fill="none"><circle cx="9" cy="9" r="8" fill="#0967d2" stroke="#0967d2" stroke-width="1"/><path d="M9 5v4M9 13h.01" stroke="white" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
                  <p class="text-sm text-text-body leading-relaxed">Always verify DSC requirements directly with Round Rock Municipal Court before submitting anything. Court fees, deadlines, and procedures can change. Call <a href="tel:5122185480" class="text-primary hover:underline font-medium">(512) 218-5480</a> or visit <a href="https://www.roundrocktexas.gov/city-departments/municipal-court/driving-safety-courses/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-primary hover:underline">www.roundrocktexas.gov/city-departments/municipal-court/driving-safety-courses</a>.</p>
                </div>

                <p class="text-xs text-text-subtle text-right">Court information last verified: May 2026</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          )}
        </div><!-- /left col -->

        <!-- Right Column — Buy Box -->
        <div class="lg:w-[300px] flex-shrink-0">
          <div class="bg-white border border-border rounded-[20px] shadow-[0px_1px_3px_0px_rgba(17,23,34,0.04),0px_6px_16px_0px_rgba(17,23,34,0.06)] p-5 lg:sticky lg:top-[88px] flex flex-col">
            <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-3">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text leading-6 pr-2">Texas Defensive Driving Course 6hr</h3>
              <div class="bg-info px-2 py-0.5 rounded-2xl flex-shrink-0">
                <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-primary">Great Value</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-baseline gap-1 mb-1">
              <span class="text-[32px] font-bold text-text leading-9">$25</span>
              <span class="text-xs text-text-body">.00</span>
              <span class="text-lg font-medium text-text-body line-through ml-2">$35.00</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-xs text-text-body mb-3">+ $3.00 state processing fee</p>
            <div class="flex gap-1 items-center mb-4">
              {[...Array(5)].map(() => (
                <img src="/assets/icons/texas/star-pricing.svg" alt="" class="w-3.5 h-3.5" />
              ))}
              <span class="text-xs font-medium text-text ml-1">4.9 out of 5</span>
            </div>
            <a
              href={enrollUrl}
              class="w-full h-11 bg-primary hover:bg-primary-hover text-white rounded-2xl text-sm font-semibold flex items-center justify-center gap-2 no-underline transition-colors mb-3 shadow-sm"
            >
              Enroll Now
              <img src="/assets/icons/texas/arrow-enroll.svg" alt="" class="w-3 h-3" />
            </a>
            <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
              {[
                "Secure checkout",
                "TDLR-approved provider",
                "100% money-back guarantee",
                "Instant Certificate Download",
                "Compatible with any device",
              ].map(item => (
                <div class="flex gap-2 items-center">
                  <div class="bg-info rounded-full w-5 h-5 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                    <img src="/assets/icons/texas/checkmark-feature.svg" alt="" class="w-3 h-3" />
                  </div>
                  <span class="text-xs text-text-body">{item}</span>
                </div>
              ))}
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>

      </div><!-- /two col -->
    </div>
  </section>

</TexasLayout>
)}
